- TWO DAYS.

03:26.374 --> 03:27.775
- PURPOSE OF VISIT?

03:27.808 --> 03:29.777
- WE'RE DOING A BICYCLE RIDE
FOR CHARITY.

03:29.810 --> 03:31.845
- BOTH YOUR NAMES ARE ON THIS.

03:31.879 --> 03:33.981
- IT SAYS SPOUSES CAN USE
THE SAME FORM.

03:34.014 --> 03:37.518
- UM, WHILE WE WERE IN TORONTO,
OFFICER,

03:37.551 --> 03:39.453
WE TOOK ADVANTAGE OF THE FACT
THAT SAME-SEX MARRIAGES

03:39.487 --> 03:41.855
ARE LEGAL.
- SO WE TIED THE KNOT.

03:41.889 --> 03:43.991
