03:44.024 --> 03:49.863
- WHO'S HE?
both: OUR SON.

03:49.897 --> 03:52.032
- YOU KNOW, THIS MAY BE LEGAL
IN CANADA,

03:52.065 --> 03:53.667
BUT THE UNITED STATES
OF AMERICA

03:53.701 --> 03:55.403
DOESN'T RECOGNIZE GAY
MARRIAGES.

03:55.436 --> 03:56.737
- OH, COME ON, OFFICER,

03:56.770 --> 03:58.472
THEY'RE JUST A COUPLE
OF CRAZY KIDS

03:58.506 --> 04:01.542
WHO FELL IN LOVE AND GOT
HITCHED--GIVE 'EM A BREAK.

04:01.575 --> 04:03.277
- IF YOU WANT TO ENTER
THE COUNTRY,

04:03.311 --> 04:04.545
YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE TO FILL
OUT TWO SEPARATE FORMS,

04:04.578 --> 04:06.980
AS SINGLE INDIVIDUALS.
NEXT!

04:13.954 --> 04:15.623
- DID YOU BRING ANY FRUIT
INTO THE COUNTRY?

04:15.656 --> 04:19.393
- 250 OF THEM, ON BICYCLES.

04:19.427 --> 04:21.061
- THE PURPOSE OF YOUR VISIT
TO CANADA WAS

04:21.094 --> 04:24.532
"TO EXPERIENCE THE GREATEST JOY
I'VE EVER KNOWN

04:24.565 --> 04:26.834
SEEING MY GAY SON MARRY
HIS LOVER."

04:26.867 --> 04:29.036
- YOU GOT A PROBLEM
WITH THAT, BUTZ?

04:29.069 --> 04:30.571
- MA.

04:30.604 --> 04:33.073
- AS I EXPLAINED TO YOUR SON,

04:33.106 --> 04:34.642
THE GOVERNMENT
OF THE UNITED STATES

04:34.675 --> 04:37.044
DOESN'T RECOGNIZE GAYS
GETTING MARRIED.

04:37.077 --> 04:41.382
- BUT YOU DO RECOGNIZE
BRITNEY SPEARS

04:41.415 --> 04:42.916
GETTING LOADED AND MARRIED
ONE NIGHT,

04:42.950 --> 04:45.853
AND HAVING IT ANNULLED
THE NEXT MORNING.

04:45.886 --> 04:47.655
OR TWO TOTAL STRANGERS
GETTING MARRIED

04:47.688 --> 04:50.558
FOR A MILLION FUCKIN' BUCKS
ON TELEVISION.

04:50.591 --> 04:52.526
IS THAT THE SANCTITY
OF MARRIAGE

04:52.560 --> 04:54.061
