- I HAD THESE MOCKED UP
JUST TO GET A FEEL.

05:28.462 --> 05:30.964
- HUH. IT FEELS UNREAL.

05:30.998 --> 05:32.966
- FOR NOW, BUT NOT FOR LONG.

05:33.000 --> 05:36.570
I ALSO ASKED A PRODUCTION
DESIGNER I HAVE IN MIND

05:36.604 --> 05:39.106
TO DO A RENDERING
OF RAGE'S LAIR.

05:39.139 --> 05:42.576
