05:42.610 --> 05:46.447
- UH...
IT'S GOOD.

05:46.480 --> 05:48.582
- IT NEEDS TO BE DARKER.

05:48.616 --> 05:50.718
NOT DARK SCARY, BUT DARK SEXY.

05:50.751 --> 05:53.587
A PLACE YOU DREAM
OF GETTING FUCKED IN.

05:53.621 --> 05:55.489
