MORE CENTER,

05:55.523 --> 05:57.458
AND RAISED, LIKE AN ALTAR.

05:57.491 --> 06:00.060
SINCE RAGE'S SEXUAL ENERGY IS
WHAT MOTIVATES THE CHARACTER

06:00.093 --> 06:01.629
