- IT'S FINE.

07:20.240 --> 07:23.110
- WELL, HOW ARE YOUR MEAT BALLS?
- THEY'RE BOTH FINE.

07:23.143 --> 07:26.880
- WELL, SOMETHING'S NOT FINE.

07:26.914 --> 07:28.582
- TOMORROW'S MY BIRTHDAY.

07:28.616 --> 07:29.950
- UNLESS YOU'VE BEEN REBORN,

07:29.983 --> 07:31.218
