YOUR STRENGTH TOO.

08:20.968 --> 08:23.871
- GODDAMN BORDER GUARD
NOT LETTING YOU IN!

08:23.904 --> 08:26.306
HE WAS JUST FOLLOWING THE LAW.

08:26.339 --> 08:28.809
MARRIAGE DOESN'T EXIST.
AT LEAST, NOT FOR US, NOT HERE.

08:28.842 --> 08:31.745
- BUT IT WILL. ONCE THE SNOWBALL
STARTS ROLLING,

08:31.779 --> 08:34.748
THERE'S NO WAY TO STOP IT.
- THIS WAY.

08:34.782 --> 08:38.151
