- A LOT OF GOOD THAT DOES ME.

12:09.529 --> 12:10.764
IT'S NOT EVEN ON OUR ROUTE.

12:10.798 --> 12:14.868
- NO, BUT IF WE VEER OFF HERE,

12:14.902 --> 12:17.137
