- HEY, SPORT. HOW YOU DOING?

12:44.898 --> 12:47.000
- NEVER SHOULD HAVE HAD THAT
SECOND PIECE OF WEDDING CAKE.

12:47.034 --> 12:48.468
[groans]

12:48.501 --> 12:51.071
- BUT WHEN THE LOVE OF YOUR LIFE
MARRIES SOMEBODY ELSE,

12:51.104 --> 12:52.439
