14:04.978 --> 14:06.479
- AND THEN WE'LL SEND YOU HOME.

14:06.513 --> 14:08.148
- EXCUSE ME?

14:08.181 --> 14:10.250
- WE'RE GOING TO TAKE YOU IN
FOR SOME X-RAYS,

14:10.283 --> 14:14.654
